{"tid":207842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賊王末路】臨終之日 前特首曾蔭權同房作伴","createTime":"2017-04-19T06:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T10:45:05.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"655fe2fd88789ca4a688d56fba94f2c5105a2a63","tid":207842,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170419/large/1492584069_5cdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170419%2Flarge%2F1492584069_5cdd.jpg&h=482ee21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一代「賊王」葉繼歡，因癌病於今晨在瑪麗醫院羈留病房離世。當時同房階下囚，還有因公職人員行為失當罪成而被判入獄20個月的前特首曾蔭權。曾蔭權上周病發入院，至今仍在瑪麗醫院羈留病房治理。<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院羈留病房位於瑪麗醫院J座9樓，有病床22張，在囚人士類別為各懲教院所醫生轉介的男性患病在囚人士。親屬可每日上午九時至下午五時探訪，但需要在探訪時間結束前三十分鐘辦理登記。而公事探訪則逢星期六下午及公眾假期暫停服務。"},{"pid":"f7e35d692cc74aee2d985becf45ece67eb2f9aa4","tid":207842,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賊都吹捧？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今時今日，好多賣港狗一早賊都不如仲多人吹捧啦5毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"577addfde05e699f3f496c1d20de467b10985c72","tid":207842,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4838a7377cdb8164e851201ab2ebb879875b9002","tid":207842,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"天意難料"},{"pid":"1de6c701a9d9a415facedbfebcfe241957a695cf","tid":207842,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}